data.title: Temple University
data.meta_description: The official Hall of Fame for the Temple University Owls
data.text:
The Temple University Athletics Hall of Fame was established in 1969 as a means of recognizing Templeâ€™s most outstanding student-athletes across all sport programs and athletic administration.

Each member of the Temple University Athletics Hall of Fame stands as a tribute to the high standards of excellence for which Temple University Athletics has long been renowned. On behalf of Temple University, we applaud the men and women of our Hall of Fame for their achievements, both in athletics and beyond, and thank them for laying a foundation of greatness for our current and future Owls.

Temple Athletics acknowledges and thanks our Hall of Fame Committee:

President Richard Englert
